CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[CreateNewPost]
	-- Add the parameters for the stored procedure here
	(@UserEmail nvarchar(max),
	 @Company nvarchar(max),
	  @Title nvarchar (max),
	   @Content nvarchar (max),
	    @CategoryID int,
		 @DateTime datetime,
		  @IsApproved bit,
		   @IsHidden bit,
		    @PostID int output)
AS
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO Posts (UserEmail, Company, Title, Content, CategoryID, [DateTime], IsApproved, IsHidden)
    VALUES (@UserEmail, @Company, @Title, @Content, @CategoryID, @DateTime, @IsApproved, @IsHidden);
	SET @PostID = SCOPE_IDENTITY();
END
